T1	Intervention 61 440	To evaluate whether the inhibitory control of TSH and the stimulatory control of prolactin (PRL) secretion exerted by endogenous serotonin was altered in obesity, 22 obese men and 10 normal controls were tested with TRH (200 micrograms IV bolus) in the presence (experimental test) and absence (control test) of the serotonergic agonist fenfluramine (60 mg PO 90 min before TRH).
